{Experimental interface for entering "numeric bands" in response to [this User Interface StackExchange question](http://ui.stackexchange.com/questions/2898/how-to-create-bands-of-number-ranges-for-a-field)}

[heading {Overview Video}]

[youtube https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dKoWeRiIJfI 560x315]

[heading {Live Demo}]

{There's an online demo you can try out.  Bear in mind it was written in an evening, and was my first jQuery program.}

http://jquery-numband.hostilefork.com/demo/

{It's MIT licensed...in case anyone feels there's a reason to borrow anything from it!}

